*{{audio|en-us-possible.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Adjective===
'''possible'''  ({{compar}}: '''more possible''', {{superl}}: '''most possible''')

# [[Able]] but not [[certain]] to happen.
#: ''Rain tomorrow is '''possible''', but I wouldn't bet on it.''
#: ''It's not just '''possible''', it's probable.''
# Being [[considered]] for a [[position]].
#: ''Jones and Smith are both '''possible''' for the opening in sales.''
# Not [[impossible]]. 
#: ''It's '''possible'''. It might happen.''

